ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It's a class in which you learn how to prepare a presentation and how to deal with your main problems when presenting in front of an English-native audience. It provides a space for international students to boost their confidence and improve in presentation skills. I would highly recommend it!

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It helped me to prepare for future presentations and confidences and to identify my main difficulties and learn how to solve them.
